00:34:41,019 --> 00:34:51,599
[SPEAKER_02] Znagom vjeri, gore primješta, bez ljubavi ja ništa sam.

431
00:34:51,599 --> 00:35:01,139
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubav je zdrnjiva, da bodje doblosti i do.

432
00:35:01,139 --> 00:35:08,519
[SPEAKER_02] O lome zrani i ti neklo sta se ne upali.

433
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:23,619
[SPEAKER_02] Nije napristana, svoje neotraži, nije razdražljiva, oprošte zlo zaboravlja.

434
00:35:23,619 --> 00:35:32,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ključna riječ. Zlo me zaboravlja.

435
00:35:32,500 --> 00:35:38,679
[SPEAKER_00] Da. Pjesmina, pjesmama, meni najdraža rečenica.

436
00:35:39,280 --> 00:35:43,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ljubav je jača od smrti. Ljubav je jača od smrti.

437
00:35:43,639 --> 00:35:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] I zato govorim, u mom srcu, u tvom, nema ljubav.

438
00:35:48,039 --> 00:35:52,320
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo cimbalko izveći. Cimbalko izveći.

439
00:35:52,320 --> 00:35:56,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, zato nismo optični, nismo privlačni.

440
00:35:56,480 --> 00:36:01,840
[SPEAKER_00] Vratit ću se na ono koji se sada sigurno pita, ta hrpava se sigurno tu,

441
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] koji će me i sutra pitat pitanjima.

442
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:07,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam ovo, ja sam ono, ale ne osjećam, tra, la, la, la, la.

443
00:36:07,679 --> 00:36:12,260
[SPEAKER_00] I ono, drugo pitanje, a dobro, došava mi se u životu to, to, to i to.

444
00:36:12,260 --> 00:36:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ovako.

445
00:36:14,199 --> 00:36:19,679
[SPEAKER_00] Vi, koji ne tražite, koji izričito nestaneš pred gospodina i kaži,

446
00:36:19,679 --> 00:36:23,239
[SPEAKER_00] gledaj gospodine, sorry, imam kameno srce, pomagaj.

447
00:36:23,239 --> 00:36:28,699
[SPEAKER_00] A hrpa je onih oholih katolika, oholih kršćana,

448
00:36:28,699 --> 00:36:30,860
[SPEAKER_00] koji to nestanu pred Boga.

449
00:36:30,860 --> 00:36:34,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ne traže uopće milost Božju da Bog promijeni srce.

450
00:36:34,380 --> 00:36:37,400
[SPEAKER_00] Jer oni misliju da su top, oni misliju da su cool.

451
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:42,619
[SPEAKER_00] I znate koji meni ljudima najteže pomoć kad me dođu na savjet ili razgovor?

452
00:36:42,619 --> 00:36:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] Onima koji kažu, gledaj, ti, taj, taj i taj mi je to napravio,

453
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:50,599
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, on je svaki dan u crkvi.

454
00:36:50,599 --> 00:36:55,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, baš taj koji svaki dan je u prvom redu u klupi.

455
00:36:55,199 --> 00:36:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] I kako objasniti ljudima?

456
00:36:59,019 --> 00:37:02,219
[SPEAKER_00] Jer takav koji je svaki dan u klupi u crkvi,

457
00:37:02,219 --> 00:37:04,780
[SPEAKER_00] ne danas, ne kroz ovo vrijeme.

458
00:37:04,780 --> 00:37:07,639
[SPEAKER_00] Taj koji se udara o prsa, objavlje statuse,

459
00:37:07,639 --> 00:37:09,679
[SPEAKER_00] he, bez, kršćanske,

460
00:37:09,679 --> 00:37:13,280
[SPEAKER_00] a kod kući joj možda razapinjemo druge,

461
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] u društvu pljujemo po drugima,

462
00:37:16,500 --> 00:37:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] uskraćujemo ljubav drugima,

463
00:37:19,579 --> 00:37:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] vrijeme i pažnju,

464
00:37:21,559 --> 00:37:24,219
[SPEAKER_00] a svaki dan smo u crkvi.

465
00:37:24,219 --> 00:37:27,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kako? Objasniti.

466
00:37:29,019 --> 00:37:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] Oni nemaju potrebu tražiti.

467
00:37:31,699 --> 00:37:33,300
[SPEAKER_00] Milost Božje.

468
00:37:33,300 --> 00:37:35,219
[SPEAKER_00] E, sada ću vam reći.

469
00:37:35,219 --> 00:37:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] Šta gospode radi sa takvim?

470
00:37:37,039 --> 00:37:41,260
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi se već raz sigurno pitate,

471
00:37:41,260 --> 00:37:43,980
[SPEAKER_00] a zašto me zadesilo to i to?

472
00:37:43,980 --> 00:37:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto koronavirus?

473
00:37:45,639 --> 00:37:46,719
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto potres?

474
00:37:46,719 --> 00:37:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto boles?

475
00:37:48,559 --> 00:37:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto gubitak ovoga?

476
00:37:50,019 --> 00:37:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto pad u ovome?

477
00:37:51,900 --> 00:37:53,219
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto pad u onome?

478
00:37:53,219 --> 00:37:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] Evo sad odgovor ću ti dati.

479
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] Poslušaj riječ Božje.

480
00:37:59,019 --> 00:38:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] Čitam iz knjige Otkrivenja,

481
00:38:02,539 --> 00:38:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] koja mi je temelj za argument.

482
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ne kaže Stjepan, riječ Božje.

483
00:38:06,980 --> 00:38:09,239
[SPEAKER_00] Knjiga Otkrivenja, četvrto poglavlje.

484
00:38:10,039 --> 00:38:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ti tvrdiš, bogat sam,

485
00:38:12,599 --> 00:38:15,280
[SPEAKER_00] nagomilao sam bogatstvo,

486
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:17,019
[SPEAKER_00] ništa mi ne treba,

487
00:38:17,019 --> 00:38:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] a ne znaš da si upravo ti nesretan,

488
00:38:20,440 --> 00:38:21,820
[SPEAKER_00] i bijedan,

489
00:38:21,820 --> 00:38:23,579
